{{Infobox_NPC |name = Strider |image = Strider.png |personality = |time_active = Anytime |gender = Male |race = [[Keves]]i human |age = 7th Term |location = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Colony 11]]) }} '''Strider''' is a NPC in {{XC3}}. Strider can be found in [[Colony 11]].
== Overview == Strider is a part of Colony 11's assault squad alongside [[Widow]] under the command of their captain [[Zoren]]. He is the scout of the squad, and very talented at tracking footprints.
== Affinity == * [[Widow]] * [[Zoren]] * [[Knoquehardt]] {{clr}}
