{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Strikechief Alfead |image = Strikechief Alfead.jpg |caption = Strikechief Alfead |category = Minor Enemy |type = [[Tirkin]] |level = 98 |area = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Demihuman Gutter]]) |spawntime = Spawned by [[King Krawkin]] |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = |gold = |hp = |strength = |healing = |dexterity = |agility = |physdef = |ethdef = |critrate = |guardrate-front = |guardrate-side = |guardrate-back = }} '''Strikechief Alfead''' is a Minor Enemy in {{XC3}}. It is a member of the [[Tirkin]] family, and can be found at level 98 at [[Demihuman Gutter]] in the [[Erythia Sea]], and is summoned by [[King Krawkin]]'s Royal Orders art. When summoned, it will use an art on the party and then immediately disappear from the battle. {{clr}}
